                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17881210-34-off152 t17881210-34-cd153"></join> last, and putting him in fear, and feloniously taking from his person, and against his will, six men's hats, value 3 l. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17881210-34-victim274" type="victimName">
                           Richard 
